issue.title: chore(API & extension): Update the path for accessing the API
issue.body:
- Update the path for API access.
  - Previously path was ://getcouper.com:8000/*
  - New path ://getcouper.com:8000/api/*
- The server's routes have been updated to reflect this change.
- The extension's API access path has been updated.
- Moved the "site" files from "/site" in the repo to "/site/old".

issue.title: When there is only 1 bookmark in a group, that bookmark is NOT deleted from the table.
issue.body:
When there is only **1** bookmark in a group, that bookmark is **NOT** deleted from the table. If another group is joined, That single bookmark from the previous group is added to the bottom of the bookmarks of the new group.

This **ONLY** exists when there is just **ONE** bookmark in a group.
